text: Calico is a research and development biotech company. It was started on September 18, 2013 by Google and Arthur D. Levinson. Its goal is to fight aging and diseases associated with aging. == References == == Other websites == * https://www.calicolabs.com/ Category:Google Category:Gerontology Category:Research organizations in the United States Category:2013 establishments in the United States Category:Biotechnology companies of the United States
